Use a funnel chart to visualize sequential data that can be broken up into stages, such as a sales cycle.

Create a Funnel Chart
In the lens, click  and then select the Funnel chart type.
In the Segment Size field, add the measure that determines the size of each segment.
In the Segments field, add the dimension to group the data by.
To change the chart display, click  and set the chart properties in the Formatting panel.
title: Creating Funnel Charts with Salesforce Analytics
